parameters:
Do you want to put the Crown of the Dead back into the
treasure chest?
Clea (Let's do it after we prepare)
Clea: With this... the request is complete, right?

Tailor Nora: I've seen something amazing! Seeing skeletons
moving around was the best experience!

Mage Relm: Moving with telekinesis...? No way, no way, I
have no idea about the principles at all.

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, I knew it was an evil spirit,
right?

Mage Relm: Only religious people believe in things like
that! Mages value understanding... What are you doing!?

Tailor Nora: I wanted to write down my inspiration! I found
some really good charcoal, so with this--
ピクチャのアニメーション準備 19 3 連番 0
ピクチャのループアニメーション開始 1 1
ピクチャのアニメーション終了 1
Clea: Nora-san, please move away from there!

Thief Nora: Oh, I hear a sound! The bones are gathering
again and starting to regenerate!
Clea: Let's run away in times like this!

Tailor Nora: I-I understand! Come on, let's escape from
here quickly!
